Package: pwSEM
Title: Piecewise Structural Equation Modelling
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bill", "Shipley", , "Bill.Shipley@USherbrooke.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7026-3880"))
Description: Conduct dsep tests (piecewise SEM) of a directed, or mixed, acyclic graph 
    without latent variables (but possibly with implicitly marginalized or
    conditioned latent variables that create dependent errors) based on
    linear, generalized linear, or additive modelswith or without a
    nesting structure for the data. Also included are functions to do desp tests
    step-by-step,exploratory path analysis, and Monte Carlo X2 probabilities.
    This package accompanies Shipley, B, (2026).Cause and Correlation in Biology:
     A User's Guide to Path Analysis, StructuralEquations and
     Causal Inference (3rd edition).  Cambridge University Press.
